Class S3KiraDB

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class S3KiraDB
extends KiraDb
    Construct an Amazon S3-backed instance of KiraDb. The constructors require the usual Amazon AWS S3 key, secret, and bucket name.
    Author:
    David Beckemeyer and Mark Petrovic
